dcterms:description: VoxCeleb2 is composed of short speech clips extracted from interview videos uploaded to Youtube, containing a development set with 1,092,009 utterances for 5,994 celebrities and a test set with 36,237 utterances for 118 celebrities.
dcterms:title: VoxCeleb2

dcterms:description: An in-house dataset consisting of 345,000 music tracks of various genres, divided into a training set of 340,000 tracks and a test set of 5,000 tracks.
dcterms:title: Music Tracks (In-house dataset)
